表格派工单明细的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('DispatchOrderDetail')
and type = 'U')
drop table DispatchOrderDetail
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: DispatchOrderDetail */
/*==============================================================*/
create table DispatchOrderDetail (
ID int identity(1,1),
MasterID int null,
DispatchNo varchar(50) null,
StartDate datetime null,
EndDate datetime null,
Qty int null constraint DF_DispatchOrderDetail_Qty default (0)
)
ON [PRIMARY]
END
go
